<div class="fullpage">
  <h4>Nag All "Waiting on User" Tickets</h4>
  <p class="instructions">
    Click below to send a gentle reminder to the users you're waiting on.
    <i class="material-icons tooltipped tiny" data-delay="40" data-tooltip="We remind your users by adding a public comment to each ticket in the 'Waiting on user' state.">info_outline</i>
  </p>
  <button id="send_nags" class="waves-effect waves-light btn">
    <i class="material-icons right">email</i> Send Nags
  </button>

  <hr class="space-it"/>
  <h4>User Nag Settings</h4>
  <ul class="collapsible popout" data-collapsible="accordion">
    <li class="nag-text">
      <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">chat</i>Nag Text</div>
      <div class="collapsible-body">
        <p>Specify the reminder text we should use to nag your users.</p>
        <%= form_tag nag_text_path, {method: :put, remote: true, id: "nag_text_form"} do %>
          <%= hidden_field_tag :site, ''%>
          <p class="input-field">
            <i class="material-icons prefix">mode_edit</i>
            <textarea id="nag_text" name="nag_text" class="materialize-textarea"><%= @nag_text %></textarea>
            <label for="nag_text">Nag Message</label>
          </p>
          <p class="card-action">
            <button id="change_text" class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">Submit
              <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
            </button>
          </p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="nag-history">
      <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">done_all</i>Nag History</div>
      <div class="collapsible-body">
        <%= render partial: 'home/nag_history' %>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">portable_wifi_off</i>No Nag List</div>
      <div class="collapsible-body"><p>These people or tickets won't be nagged.</p><p>Coming soon...</p></div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">pause_circle_outline</i>Auto-Close</div>
      <div class="collapsible-body"><p>They <i>still</i> haven't responded? It must not be that important.  Let's close this after one last nag.</p><p>Coming soon...</p></div>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="space-it"/>
  <div class="card teal lighten-3">
    <div class="card-content">
      <span class="card-title">User Nag Feedback</span>
      <p>Let us know what you like or don't like.  And please tell us what future features you most want.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-action">
      <%= mail_to 'support@spiceworks.com', subject: 'User Nag App Feedback', class: 'white-text' do %>
        <i class="material-icons">question_answer</i>Email Us
      <% end %>
      <a class="white-text" href="https://community.spiceworks.com/appcenter/app/extension_43" target="_blank"><i class="material-icons">grade</i>Write a Review</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<%= javascript_tag "UserNag.ticketPlacement = false;" %>
